> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                            pixel format                           | 12
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                               width                               | 16
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                               height                              | 20
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                          frame_rate_numer                         | 24
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                          frame_rate_denom                         | 28
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |    num_bufs    |                     reserved                     | 32
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                              reserved                             | 36
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
