> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |   num_planes   |                     reserved                     | 16
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                          plane_offset[0]                          | 20
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                          plane_offset[1]                          | 24
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                          plane_offset[2]                          | 28
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                          plane_offset[3]                          | 32
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
