> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |         plane_stride[2]         |         plane_stride[3]         | 56
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
> + * |                              reserved                             | 60
> + * +----------------+----------------+----------------+----------------+
